9️⃣ How You Should THINK Before Solving Matrix Problems

Always ask:

1️⃣ How many rows?
2️⃣ How many columns?
3️⃣ Which direction to move?
4️⃣ Which index changes? i or j
5️⃣ Any condition like i == j?

👉 Thinking > Coding

